Although moderate profit can be made off teak logs, there is still a market for them. Players often use these logs for Firemaking and Construction.

Teak trees are far out, but the best place is the woodland south-west of Castle Wars. Depending on levels, players can chop 550-1,200 teak logs (111,650-243,600 coins) per hour.

Another good method for players looking to gather teak logs is to plant 3 teak trees at Fossil Island and use the agility shortcut (requires level 70 agility) to bank logs.
